 and is based in new york city epoch investment partners inc operates as a subsidiary of td bank us holding company detailed description  park avenuenew york ny united statesfounded in  employees phone  fax  wwweipnycom key executives for epoch investment partners inc mr william wallace priest jr cpa cfa chief executive officer  cochief investment officer age  mr timothy torrey taussig cofounder president chief operating officer  director age  mr david n pearl cfa cofounder cocio executive vp head of us equities  portfolio manager age  mr adam borak cpa chief financial officer principal accounting officer  secretary age  mr mark mcgowan managing director  chief technology officer compensation as of fiscal year  epoch investment partners inc key developments epoch investment partners inc presents at the art of successful investing conference oct  am sep   epoch investment partners inc presents at the art of successful investing conference oct  am venue the metropolitan club  e th st new york ny  new york united states speakers william wallace priest chief executive officer cochief investment officer managing director portfolio manager and director td asset management inc appoints epoch investment partners inc as portfolio adviser for td private international stock fund aug   td asset management inc tdam announced a portfolio adviser change for the td private international stock fund effective on or about september   epoch investment partners inc epoch will join tdam to serve as a portfolio adviser to the fund bill booth cfa managing director and portfolio manager for epoch will focus on achieving the fundamental objectives of the fund by primarily investing in international developed market equities similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions avai